---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../components/Breadcrumbs.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Disclaimer"
  description="Important information about the limits of the guidance published on Electrician Times and the need to use qualified electricians."
  canonical="/disclaimer/"
>
  <Breadcrumbs items={[{ name: 'Home', href: '/' }, { name: 'Disclaimer' }]} />
  <div class="container page-body">
    <h1>Disclaimer</h1>
    <p>
      The content on Electrician Times is provided for general informational and educational
      purposes only. It is not professional advice, and it does not replace the training,
      qualifications and local code knowledge of a licensed electrician.
    </p>

    <h2>No professional relationship</h2>
    <p>
      Reading this website does not create any professional or contractual relationship between
      you and Electrician Times or its authors.
    </p>

    <h2>Electrical work is dangerous</h2>
    <p>
      Working with electricity can cause serious injury, fire or death. Never work on live
      circuits. Requirements for electrical installations differ by country and region — always
      follow the regulations that apply where you live, and hire a licensed, qualified electrician
      for installations, repairs and inspections.
    </p>

    <h2>Accuracy</h2>
    <p>
      We work to keep articles accurate and current, but we make no warranties about completeness
      or fitness for a particular purpose. Product details, prices and regulations change over
      time.
    </p>

    <h2>External links</h2>
    <p>
      Articles may link to third-party websites, including contributor and guest-post links. We are
      not responsible for the content or practices of external sites.
    </p>

    <p>
      Questions about this disclaimer? <a href="/contact-us/">Contact us</a>.
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
